        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "重的物体比轻的物体下落得更快。 下落速度与重量成正比。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_294abfafb84132f1",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_a9ca4fd9f5070274",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "在日常空气环境中，从同一高度落下时，石头通常比羽毛更早落地； 重物看起来往往比轻物下落得更快。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_c2f24a14911f9a97",
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_4106b1710e46373e",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "env"
        },
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "law"
        }
      ],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "在 {env} 中暂时接受 {law}： 轻球天然比重球下落更慢。于是当轻球与重球绑在一起时， 轻球应当拖慢重球，复合体 HL 的下落速度应慢于单独的重球 H。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_4c530ed4b621d5b7",
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_66d50713e601243e",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "prediction_a"
        },
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "prediction_b"
        }
      ],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "比较 {prediction_a} 与 {prediction_b}。 这两条结论针对同一个绑球系统、同一时刻、同一环境， 却分别断言“更慢”和“更快”，因此不能同时为真。 这暴露出亚里士多德落体定律在该思想实验中的内在矛盾。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_34cabc42c0253a55",
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_d6c7bca7e8a06693",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "gradient"
        },
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "observation"
        }
      ],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "由 {gradient} 可知，介质越稀薄，轻重物体的速度差异越小。 因而 {observation} 更应被解释为介质阻力造成的表象， 而不是重量本身决定自由落体速度的证据。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_f0cc0fa5de32b098",
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_422bad5b75dd2df5",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "confound"
        },
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "env"
        },
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "support"
        },
        {
          "constraint": "unknown",
          "name": "verdict"
        }
      ],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "如果 {verdict}，并且 {confound}，再加上 {support}， 那么在 {env} 这一无空气阻力的极限条件下， 最合理的预测是：不同重量的物体应以相同速率下落。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_d02452d248c12ef9",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_8ca9a2b93b0e9307",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "复合体 HL 因轻球拖拽，下落速度应慢于单独的重球 H。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_6bac07256347fe0a",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_a95c07b51e050bfb",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "复合体 HL 总重量大于单独的重球 H，下落速度应快于 H。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_a8ddd1deb184e365",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "contradiction",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_b6bb05362b879e90",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "between": [
          "tied_pair_slower_than_heavy",
          "tied_pair_faster_than_heavy"
        ]
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "同一定律对同一绑球系统同时预测\"更慢\"和\"更快\"，自相矛盾。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_8a0444d0fbd186ea",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_148c1b8d98f495b5",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "亚里士多德\"重者下落更快\"的定律因绑球矛盾而不能成立。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_676b82d2e13da730",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_292f81b065df5b91",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "在水、油、空气等不同介质中比较轻重物体的下落， 会发现介质越稠密，速度差异越明显；介质越稀薄，差异越不明显。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_111e7631f5fe6000",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_1e3724075272f3b5",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "介质越稀薄，轻重物体的下落速度差异越小。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_3e3eba712a1b71b4",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_61197e996f3dd38a",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "日常观察到的速度差异来自空气阻力，而非重量本身。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_31c65c0054b04dbc",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_3d20684fe585a228",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "伽利略的斜面实验把下落过程放慢到可测量尺度后显示： 不同重量的小球在相同斜面条件下呈现近似一致的加速趋势， 与“重量越大速度越大”的简单比例律并不相符。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_e8ed07e04b746265",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_315917e2f79d7ef7",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "斜面实验支持\"重量不是决定落体速度的首要因素\"。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_879e5224d1b987f8",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_cfb4e927e732fb7b",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "在真空中，不同重量的物体应以相同速率下落。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_26e5a61b530de034",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "question",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_716c8ef657abaf41",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "能否在足够接近真空的条件下直接比较重球与轻球的下落时间？ 如果日常差异确实来自空气阻力，那么真正决定性的实验应当在几乎无介质的环境中完成。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_c5316238592f296a",
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_25dddf57cc6aae0d",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "chain": "drag_prediction_chain",
        "elaborated_from": "deduce_drag_effect"
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "在 想象一个重球 H 和一个轻球 L 从同一高度落下。 先分别考虑它们各自的“自然下落速度”，再考虑把二者用细绳绑成 复合体 HL 后一起下落，会得到什么结果。 中暂时接受 重的物体比轻的物体下落得更快。 下落速度与重量成正比。： 轻球天然比重球下落更慢。于是当轻球与重球绑在一起时， 轻球应当拖慢重球，复合体 HL 的下落速度应慢于单独的重球 H。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_c90a9fc2bd369242",
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_8c42bbb2570499b9",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "chain": "contradiction_chain",
        "elaborated_from": "expose_mutual_exclusion"
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "比较 复合体 HL 因轻球拖拽，下落速度应慢于单独的重球 H。 与 复合体 HL 总重量大于单独的重球 H，下落速度应快于 H。。 这两条结论针对同一个绑球系统、同一时刻、同一环境， 却分别断言“更慢”和“更快”，因此不能同时为真。 这暴露出亚里士多德落体定律在该思想实验中的内在矛盾。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_222a545c894b403b",
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_645d38ebf9ed901b",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "chain": "confound_chain",
        "elaborated_from": "explain_everyday_observation"
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "由 介质越稀薄，轻重物体的下落速度差异越小。 可知，介质越稀薄，轻重物体的速度差异越小。 因而 在日常空气环境中，从同一高度落下时，石头通常比羽毛更早落地； 重物看起来往往比轻物下落得更快。 更应被解释为介质阻力造成的表象， 而不是重量本身决定自由落体速度的证据。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_e20139e91ca72fbd",
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_1f43c2bad5e7676d",
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "chain": "synthesis_chain",
        "elaborated_from": "synthesize_equal_fall_prediction"
      },
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "galileo_falling_bodies",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "如果 亚里士多德\"重者下落更快\"的定律因绑球矛盾而不能成立。，并且 日常观察到的速度差异来自空气阻力，而非重量本身。，再加上 斜面实验支持\"重量不是决定落体速度的首要因素\"。， 那么在 一个理想化的无空气阻力环境， 只保留重力作用，不让介质阻力参与落体过程。 这一无空气阻力的极限条件下， 最合理的预测是：不同重量的物体应以相同速率下落。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_24b73863a5566189",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_fdc52d5c5fdf2374",
          "package": "newton_principia",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "newton_principia",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "牛顿第一定律（惯性定律）：不受外力作用的物体保持静止或匀速直线运动。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_527d75708bd777b8",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_c0c476d32d805f12",
          "package": "newton_principia",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "newton_principia",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "牛顿第二定律：物体的加速度与所受合外力成正比、与惯性质量成反比。 F = m_i × a，其中 m_i 是惯性质量。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_36e2dbc421a94c06",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_2c502bb54f9d83c6",
          "package": "newton_principia",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "newton_principia",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "牛顿第三定律（作用与反作用定律）：两个物体之间的力总是大小相等、方向相反。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_66a735381c83609f",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_d8fc78dec7817285",
          "package": "newton_principia",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "newton_principia",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "万有引力定律：任意两个物体之间存在引力，大小为 F = G × M × m_g / r²， 其中 m_g 是引力质量，M 是地球质量，r 是距离，G 是引力常数。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_5064d0948e80f13d",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "claim",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_1a3d5bc005ab292d",
          "package": "newton_principia",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "newton_principia",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "惯性质量与引力质量在实验精度范围内相等：m_i = m_g。 这是一个经验事实，牛顿注意到了它但没有给出理论解释。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_45eef221d0ddbd23",
      "kind": null,
      "knowledge_type": "setting",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_3c4eaab5efff7e66",
          "package": "newton_principia",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "metadata": null,
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package": "newton_principia",
          "version": "1.0.0"
        }
      ],
      "representative_content": "在地球表面附近，距离 r 近似等于地球半径 R， 因而引力加速度 g = GM/R² 可视为常数（约 9.8 m/s²）。\n"
    },
    {
      "global_canonical_id": "gcn_289afd3dfbc9eb63",
      "kind": "infer_action",
      "knowledge_type": "action",
      "member_local_nodes": [
        {
          "local_canonical_id": "lcn_796d71209059ab17",
